    "pseudocode":  "FLOW Microflow: MxModelReflection.IVK_RecalculateSize\r\nNODES=5; EDGES=4\r\n1. START\r\n2. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve DbSizeEstimateList from MxModelReflection.DbSizeEstimate\r\n3. LOOP iterate DbSizeEstimateList as Estimate\r\n  4. LOOP BODY\r\n    5. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve MxObjectMemberList from MxModelReflection.MxObjectMember\r\n    6. ACTION AggregateListAction: AggregateListAction (output=count, errorHandlingType=Rollback)\r\n    7. ACTION ChangeObjectAction: change Estimate (CalculatedSizeInBytes=$Size, CalculatedSizeInKiloBytes=ceil($Size : 1024); refreshInClient=false)\r\n    8. ACTION CreateVariableAction: create variable Size=8 + $count\r\n    9. LOOP iterate MxObjectMemberList as Member\r\n      10. LOOP BODY\r\n        11. DECISION expression=$ValueType/TypeEnum\r\n        12. ACTION ChangeVariableAction: change variable Size=$Size + 1\r\n        13. NODE ContinueEvent: ContinueEvent\r\n        14. ACTION ChangeVariableAction: change variable Size=$Size + 8\r\n        15. NODE ExclusiveMerge: ExclusiveMerge\r\n        16. ACTION ChangeVariableAction: change variable Size=$Size + 2+( ceil(if $Member/FieldLength != empty then $Member/FieldLength * 0.8 else 200) *2)\r\n        17. NODE ExclusiveMerge: ExclusiveMerge\r\n        18. ACTION ChangeVariableAction: change variable Size=$Size + 2+(20*2)\r\n        19. ACTION ChangeVariableAction: change variable Size=$Size + 2+(68*2)\r\n        20. ACTION ChangeVariableAction: change variable Size=$Size + 36\r\n        21. ACTION MicroflowCallAction: call microflow MxModelReflection.Log -\u003e LogProduct\r\n        22. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve ValueType over association MxObjectMember_Type from Member\r\n        23. ACTION ChangeVariableAction: change variable Size=$Size + 4\r\n        24. DECISION has owner or changed by expression=contains( toLowerCase($Member/CompleteName), \u0027owner\u0027) or contains( toLowerCase($Member/CompleteName), \u0027changedby\u0027)\r\n 